OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry but cloudy morning with
OL,6,Flow cloud and some misty patches
OL,7,Fpossible, brighter spells along the
OL,8,FMoray Coast where it will warm. Cloud
OL,9,Fbreaking up from late morning to give
OL,10,Fsome long sunny spells in the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry evening with late
OL,14,Fsunshine, then long clear spells after
OL,15,Fsunset. Overnight will be dry with
OL,16,Flong clear spells, but a few mist and
OL,17,Ffog patches possibly forming.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
